pull_request.title: Add example tee commands to READMEs to capture run.sh output.
pull_request.body: Added cmds to readme to make it easier to collect run.sh output for later inclusion in the test results wiki. Some VMs don't have a shared clipboard which makes collecting results fiddly and error prone.
